@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_owpxrw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.35 + 0.15)
    tmp = wp.exp(0.55)
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v0 + 0.00 + tmp + 0.47)))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.sin(v0))
    v2 = v0
    v0 = wp.sin(0.64)
    data[tid] = v0
